CBRE Healthcare and Social Infrastructure Australia are pleased to offer for sale a unique opportunity to secure a long-term healthcare investment on a highly valuable landholding of 2,093sqm* located 100m* to Knox Private Hospital.

- Freestanding purpose built medical centre of 378sqm* with 8 consulting rooms, 2 specialised audio rooms, staff lunchroom, amenities, reception and waiting areas

- Irreplaceable land holding of 2,093sqm*, with dominant exposure to Mountain Highway of 40m*, favourable General Residential zoning and 42 onsite car parking spaces

- Highly desirable healthcare location, located only 100m* to Knox Private Hospital, the largest private Hospital in East Victoria, providing healthcare services to over 1.2 million people, which equates to 25%* of Victoria's population

- Immediate access to Wantirna Mall and Westfield Knox City Shopping Centre providing a range of world class retailers, cafes and restaurants and Eastlink (1km*) providing direct link to the Melbourne CBD (26km*)

- Income of $200,000 p.a + GST + outgoings with annual 3% increases, 6-month bank guarantee + personal guarantees
